title: Dell security advisory (AV25-733)
description: Between November 3 and 9, 2025, Dell published security advisories to address vulnerabilities in the following products:
products: Dell APEX Cloud Platform for Red Hat OpenShift  versions prior to 03.04.02.00
Dell Enterprise SONiC Distribution  versions prior to 4.5.1
Dell PowerSwitch S5448F-ON  versions prior to v3.52.5.1-12
Dell PowerSwitch Z9264F-ON  versions prior to 3.42.5.1-21
Dell PowerSwitch Z9432F-ON  versions prior to 3.51.5.1-21
solution: Review the references and apply the necessary updates.
